---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Lauchoy Portfolio" description="Learn about my creative journey, experience, and approach to design, photography, and creative direction.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 via-white to-accent-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-display font-bold text-primary-900 mb-6">
            About <span class="text-gradient">Me</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-primary-600 mb-8">
            Creative professional passionate about crafting meaningful visual experiences that connect, inspire, and drive results.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">8+ Years Experience</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-accent-100 text-accent-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">50+ Projects</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Global Clients</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-200 to-primary-200 rounded-3xl"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-24 h-24 bg-accent-500 rounded-2xl opacity-80"></div>
          <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-16 h-16 bg-primary-500 rounded-xl opacity-60"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-primary-900 mb-8 text-center">
          My Creative Journey
        </h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="text-xl text-primary-600 mb-6">
            My journey into the creative world began over eight years ago with a simple fascination for how visual elements could tell powerful stories and evoke emotions. What started as a curiosity quickly evolved into a passion that has shaped my career and approach to creative work.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-primary-600 mb-6">
            Based in San Francisco, I've had the privilege of working with diverse clients ranging from innovative startups to established luxury brands. Each project has taught me something new about the intersection of creativity, strategy, and human connection.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-primary-600 mb-8">
            My approach is rooted in the belief that great design isn't just about aestheticsâ€”it's about solving problems, communicating ideas clearly, and creating experiences that resonate with people on a deeper level. Whether I'm developing a brand identity, capturing a moment through photography, or designing a digital experience, I always start with understanding the story we need to tell.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Skills & Expertise -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-primary-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">
          Skills & Expertise
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A comprehensive skill set developed through years of creative practice and continuous learning.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Brand Design -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zM21 5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a4 4 0 004 4h4a2 2 0 002-2V5z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-display font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Brand Design</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-primary-600">Logo design, visual identity systems, brand guidelines, and strategic brand development.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Photography -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 9a2 2 0 012-2h.93a2 2 0 001.664-.89l.812-1.22A2 2 0 0110.07 4h3.86a2 2 0 011.664.89l.812 1.22A2 2 0 0018.07 7H19a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z"></path>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 13a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-display font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Photography</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-primary-600">Fashion, portrait, product, and commercial photography with creative direction.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Web Design -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-display font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Web Design</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-primary-600">UI/UX design, responsive development, and modern web experiences.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Creative Direction -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-display font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Creative Direction</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-primary-600">Campaign development, art direction, and strategic creative leadership.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">
          My Creative Process
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A structured approach that ensures every project delivers exceptional results.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold">1</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Discovery</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600">Understanding your goals, audience, and challenges through in-depth consultation and research.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold">2</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600">Developing a creative strategy that aligns with your objectives and resonates with your audience.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold">3</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Creation</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600">Bringing ideas to life through thoughtful design, careful execution, and attention to detail.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold">4</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Refinement</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600">Collaborative refinement and optimization to ensure the final result exceeds expectations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-primary-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">
          Core Values
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          The principles that guide every project and client relationship.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Value 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Passion</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600">Every project is approached with genuine enthusiasm and dedication to creating something meaningful.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Value 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Excellence</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600">Commitment to delivering work that not only meets but exceeds expectations in every detail.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Value 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Collaboration</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600">Working closely with clients as partners to ensure the final result truly reflects their vision.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-primary-900 text-white">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-6">
        Let's Create Together
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-primary-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Ready to bring your creative vision to life? I'd love to learn about your project and explore how we can work together.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium text-primary-900 bg-white rounded-full hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors">
          Start a Conversation
        </a>
        <a href="/work" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium text-white border-2 border-white rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-primary-900 transition-colors">
          View My Work
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
